Revision history for Mojolicious::Plugin::SemanticUI

0.17 2015-05-09
  - Updated with latest minified files from Semantic UI 1.12.2
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/archive/1.12.2.zip
  - Components (*.min.*) are back to allow using only what is needed
    and not everything.  

0.16 2015-04-19
  - Updated with latest minified files from Semantic UI 1.12.0
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/archive/1.12.0.zip

0.15 2015-03-21
  - Updated with latest minified files from Semantic UI 1.11.4
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/archive/1.11.4.zip

0.14 2015-03-02
  - Updated to Semantic UI 1.10.4 with latest minified files, downloaded from
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/archive/1.10.4.zip

0.13 2015-02-28
  - Updated to Semantic UI 1.10.2 with latest minified files, downloaded from
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/archive/1.10.2.zip

0.12 2015-02-11
  - Updated to Semantic UI 1.8.1 with latest minified files, downloaded from
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/archive/1.8.1.zip
  - From this release onward we will distribute only
    semantic.min.css, semantic.min.js and the themes folder.
    This makes the file management much easier and saves a lot of
    useless tests.


0.11 2015-01-18
  - Updated to Semantic UI 1.7.3 with latest minified files, downloaded from
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/archive/1.7.3.zip
  - Semantic Release Notes:
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/blob/1.7.3/RELEASE-NOTES.md 

0.10 2014-12-07
  - Updated to Semantic UI 1.1.2 with latest minified files from the dist folder
    in the zip file downloaded from https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/tree/1.1.2.


0.09 2014-11-28
  - Updated to Semantic UI 1.0.0 with latest minified files from the dist folder
    in the zip file downloaded from http://semantic-ui.com/.

0.08 2014-11-17
  - Updated to Semantic UI 1.0 with latest files from
    http://beta.semantic-ui.com/
  - Directory layout is changed so this update will brake previous
    installations. You need to remove old installation completely and update paths
    in your templates!

0.07 2014-10-11
  - Updated with latest files from http://beta.semantic-ui.com/
  - Does not require but works with Mojolicious 5.49.  

0.06 2014-09-21
  - Requiring only Perl 5.10.1 in test files.
  - Mentioned Ado.
  - Updated with latest files from http://beta.semantic-ui.com/

0.05 2014-09-11
  - Updated static files:
    https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI/issues/691#issuecomment-54922686
  - Improved tests.

0.04 2014-09-08
  - Reduced package size by removing duplicate themes folder.
  - Moved all the tree one level up.
  - Static files now seem usable - no more changes here expected.
  - Cleanups again, let's do some programming next time...

0.03 2014-09-07
  - More cleanups.

0.02 2014-09-07
  - Cleanups and work on CPAN related stuff.

0.01 2014-09-06
  - Initial release.
